data.description: *Seller is willing to give a credit of $5k to buy down rate or use towards closing costs and pre-paids*  Beautifully updated and tastefully decorated 3 bedroom, 1 bath home in a quiet residential neighborhood and the best part a NO FLOOD ZONE area. Enjoy peace of mind with a new roof and AC both which have been done in 2022. Featuring new exterior paint, indoor new washer and dryer  ,a large enclosed patio with electric outside and a shed perfect for extra storage. The gorgeous kitchen has solid cabinets, beautiful backsplash and stainless steel appliances. The bathroom features a newer vanity, mirror and tile. The 3rd bedroom would be perfect for an office. Located only a few min to the gorgeous sands and enjoy paddle boarding, swimming and beautiful sunsets on the Gulf of Mexico. This home is within a short drive to several parks such as Walsingham Park,Lake Seminole Park and 30 min from Tampa International airport. There is no HOA, CDD and short term rentals and boat parking is allowed.
